            then
A10:        (p*s+(1-p)*t)-s > 0 by A6,A9,XREAL_1:131;
            then
A11:        (p*s+(1-p)*t) > s by XREAL_1:49;
A12:        (f.(p*s+(1-p)*t)-f.s)*(t-s)*p =p*((t-s)*f.(p*s+(1-p)*t))-p*((
t-s)*f.s) & (f. t-f.(p*s+(1-p)*t))*(t-s)*(1-p) =(1-p)*((t-s)*f.t)-(1-p)*((t-s)*
            f.(p*s+(1-p)*t));
            t-(p*s+(1-p)*t) =p*(t-s);
