                .=Sum P1*((Sum P1)"*Sum(mlt(P1,E1)))+p1*e1
                .=Sum P1*(Sum((Sum P1)"*mlt(P1,E1)))+p1*e1 by RVSUM_1:117
                .=Sum P1*Sum(mlt((Sum P1)"*P1,E1))+p1*e1 by FINSEQOP:27;
A36:          ( Sum P1)"*Sum(mlt(P1,F1)) = Sum((Sum P1)"*mlt(P1,F1)) by
