              then
A39:          Sum P1*f.Sum(mlt((Sum P1)"*P1,E1)) + p1*f.e1 <= Sum P1*((
              Sum P1)"*Sum(mlt(P1,F1)))+p1*f.e1 by XREAL_1:8;
              P.(len P1+1) = p1 by A11,FINSEQ_1:59;
