  then
A41: REAL c= dom f by PARTFUN1:def 4;
  (for n being Element of NAT, P,E,F being Element of n-tuples_on REAL st
Sum P=1 & (for i being Element of NAT st i in dom P holds P.i >=0 & F.i=f.(E.i)
